CANON INFORMATION
From Official Spoiler Document:

"Somali pirate-to-be"

From Series (Deel 3 Dialogue, translated from Dutch):
"...and we're collecting money for children in Somalia so that they can go to pirate school and become pirates and capture oil tankers to finance their drug wars; and when I have my degree I'm moving to Somalia for an internship with a local pirate and I already bought an AK-47 off the darkweb but forgot to order the bullets, so if you know someone you know where to find me."
